[5] Valparaiso
Date: Mon 20 Feb 2012
Source: Latercer.com [edited]
http://www.latercera.com/noticia/nacional/2012/02/680-432003-9-instituto-de-salud-publica-confirma-caso-numero-16-de-virus-hanta.shtml

The Institute of Public Health confirmed this Monday afternoon [20 Feb 2012], the presence of [a] hantavirus in samples taken from a 65 year old man. This person is currently interned on the Carlos Van Buren Hospital in Valparaiso.

